					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Interesting subversion of the mole people cliche. It's so used in fiction that I at first instantly believed the mole guy. But to have it gradually revealed as a hoax is far more interesting. I particularly like the war medals that were made himself, that's what sealed it for me that it was all a farce.</p> 
