					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1091408#post-2622996</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1091408/scp-2622#post-2622996</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 15 Sep 2016 20:58:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DarkStuff</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1581620</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>A cardboard cigar box containing eleven facsimiles of military medals constructed from assorted detritus, including bottle caps, tinfoil, and twist ties.</p> </blockquote> <p>Yes, I read that all his stories are bull, but I still don't enjoy that this just comes out of the blue to say &quot;Yes, yes he is lying.&quot; Obviously he is way way out of his prime, and he is very definitely crazy and unreliable, but I think it would've been better if you left it a little open ended, because after all, he <em>did</em> have to come from <em>somewhere</em>.</p> <p>EDIT: <em>Although I guess it is forgivable, since making all his stories false</em> is <em>keeping it open ended, because now we have absolutely</em> no <em>idea where he came from, but I stand by my point.</em></p> <p><em>+1, by the way.</em></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
