					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like that he's gradually revealed to be lying about everything, but more than that I like that he was discovered while ambling around the London Underground system. (As you don't mention any TfL staff involvement, I like to think anomalies are so often found wandering aimlessly around the Tube network that the Foundation now carries out routine sweeps there&#8230;) +1 for sheer fun weirdness.</p> <p>Edit: didn't read the Addendum properly. If I could, I'd +1 again for the facsimiles of military medals - nice little emotional touch without being overly sentimental, good work.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
