					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1091408#post-2220530</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1091408/scp-2622#post-2220530</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 30 Jan 2015 18:33:11 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Eskobar</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1173523</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>If this guy's supposed to be legitimate, I'll probably neutral vote, seeing how many <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1000">other</a> former species have <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1483">claims</a> to prior dominance over the Earth, and at least one other <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1867">non-human explorer</a> of the Earth. If this is a hoax with no legitimate explanation for how the guy is what he is (since his story sounds like such bullshit), I have to upvote at that point, because what the <em>fuck</em>.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1091408#post-2220528</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1091408/scp-2622#post-2220528</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 30 Jan 2015 18:32:18 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>HotCocoaNerd</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2032511</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So here's my take on this:</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;is&nbsp;this&nbsp;the&nbsp;case?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Or&nbsp;am&nbsp;I&nbsp;the&nbsp;mad&nbsp;one?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Everything he talked about really happened, to an extent. The places and peoples described did exist, but maybe not in the places mentioned, or with the traits given. Maybe this guy even was a warrior and ambassador at one point. Unfortunately, the facts have gotten muddled as he goes crazier and crazier with age.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
